   <p xml:id="146" begin="00:04:01.563" end="00:04:03.432">SPECIFICALLY FOR HAITI.</p>
   <p xml:id="147" begin="00:04:02.731" end="00:04:07.035">&gt;&gt; ALL RIGHT.</p>
   <p xml:id="148" begin="00:04:03.498" end="00:04:09.771">IF YOU GO TO HAITI,</p>
   <p xml:id="149" begin="00:04:07.102" end="00:04:10.405">MS. DEDEFRANCIS HAVE YOU</p>
   <p xml:id="150" begin="00:04:09.838" end="00:04:11.339">BEEN THERE LATELY.</p>
   <p xml:id="151" begin="00:04:10.472" end="00:04:13.408">&gt;&gt; NOT LATELY.</p>
   <p xml:id="152" begin="00:04:11.406" end="00:04:14.342">&gt;&gt; I DONATE TO A FUND CALL</p>
