   <p xml:id="154" begin="00:04:14.409" end="00:04:15.644">FOUNDATION.</p>
   <p xml:id="155" begin="00:04:14.810" end="00:04:16.745">CAN I TELL THAT YOU COUNTRY</p>
   <p xml:id="156" begin="00:04:15.710" end="00:04:19.614">IS PROBABLY WORSE OFF NOW</p>
   <p xml:id="157" begin="00:04:16.812" end="00:04:21.750">THAN IT WAS BEFORE THE</p>
   <p xml:id="158" begin="00:04:19.681" end="00:04:22.451">EARTHQUAKE OF 2010.</p>
   <p xml:id="159" begin="00:04:21.817" end="00:04:23.952">AND $500 MILLION SHOULD HAVE</p>
