   <p xml:id="162" begin="00:04:26.455" end="00:04:30.792">THERE JUST AN OBSERVATION.</p>
   <p xml:id="163" begin="00:04:28.190" end="00:04:34.029">&gt;&gt; WELL, BILL, I WOULD SAY</p>
   <p xml:id="164" begin="00:04:30.859" end="00:04:37.265">WAS ABOUT $13 BILLION PRED</p>
   <p xml:id="165" begin="00:04:34.096" end="00:04:38.733">INTO HAITI IN MONEY OF THE</p>
