   <p xml:id="170" begin="00:04:43.638" end="00:04:46.007">&gt;&gt; KNOW I KNOW.</p>
   <p xml:id="171" begin="00:04:44.506" end="00:04:47.242">&gt;&gt; WE DID MAKE IT A LOT</p>
   <p xml:id="172" begin="00:04:46.074" end="00:04:49.211">BETTER THAN HAD IT BEEN.</p>
